ould be considered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/102669/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, More', '', 1767369485);
